snippet.title: The Void Project | Demo Release Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Description: The Void Project is a 90s-inspired FPS game with a unique art style. Instead of endless hordes of demons, the timer is you should worry about more. Complete waves and defeat demons as fast as possible to climb the leaderboard. With swift movement and powerful weapons, let's see how far you can go.

Get the Game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2681270/
Join Our Discord: https://www.discord.com/invite/YqANsCse65/
